reviews.text: I bought a plate of 牛什 for takeout at a cost of hkd71 ($1 for the take out container).   Portion is good enough for 1 person but definitely not enough for 2.  Taste is good and not as salty as some others I tried.  Their chilly sauce is quite good as well and I wish I asked for more than 1 packet.
Good beef noodle at good price. Small shop, limited seating.
$23 is quite cheap but not too tasty
Good
Traditional Hong Kong style noodles, taste good and cheap.

result.name: 嵩記牛什

reviews.text: 又係又平又低食👍
深水埗區的老牌牛什牛腩店。質素有保證, 地方較舊和窄, 不怕這方面的話值得一試。

越南雙拼河粉, 係生牛肉同牛雜.
你當佢喺牛雜河粉食就好😉千祈唔好當越南河粉的味道相比.😉. 
好大碗, 抵食😊
可惜當日我去冷氣壞了😭 熱衰人囉
此麵店食材是可以的，價錢大衆化，不防一試
